'''Pressure bombs''' were weapons used by both the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and the [[Honorable Union of Desevro and Tion|Honorable Union of Desevro & Tion]] in the [[Tionese War]]. They were designed to release a vast quantity of sheer pressure when detonated, causing widespread damage.

During the Tionese War, the weapons were first deployed by the Union navy during attacks on outlying Republic shipyards. Both sides sent fleets up and down the [[Perlemian Trade Route/Legends|Perlemian Trade Route]] and [[Orbital bombardment/Legends|bombed]] their respective capitals of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and [[Desevro/Legends|Desevro]] throughout the century-long conflict.

When the Republic mounted its last counter-offensive with a [[Republic Navy/Legends|newly-launched star fleet]], turning the tide of the conflict, they made an example of [[Desevro/Legends|Desevro]] itself, refusing the Union's offer of unconditional surrender and laying waste to the planet with a sustained pressure bombardment from orbit that left the planet in ruins.

[[LIN demolitionmech autonomous minelayer/Legends|LIN demolitionmechs]] were capable of seeding battlefields with pressure bombs or [[antirepulsorlift grenade]]s.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

[[Hethrir]] would later use pressure bombs during the [[Empire Reborn]] crisis.

